// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-0189 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 34856bb4-eb3a-5c61-9fe9-2a92b97a2cd6

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:10*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:8*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:9*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:18.04-ESM*")
